Enum NavigationManager.AudioEvent

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<NavigationManager.AudioEvent>
      • com.here.android.mpa.guidance.NavigationManager.AudioEvent
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<NavigationManager.AudioEvent>
    Enclosing class:
    NavigationManager

    public static enum NavigationManager.AudioEvent
extends java.lang.Enum<NavigationManager.AudioEvent>
    Used for enabling/disabling audio events during navigation. See NavigationManager.setEnabledAudioEvents(EnumSet).

    • Enum Constant Summary

      Enum Constants 
      Enum Constant and Description
      GPS
      GPS output (GPS lost, GPS restored).
      MANEUVER
      Maneuver output (maneuvers, stop-overs reached, destination reached).
      ROUTE
      Route output (re-routing, route recalculated).
      SAFETY_SPOT
      Safety spot audio output (approaching safety spot).
      SPEED_LIMIT
      Speed limit audio output (exceeded limit start, exceeded limit end).
      VIBRATION
      Vibration (during walk navigation only).
